GUI to automate Neural Network Regressor and Classifier Project.
How this GUI works?
 Execute the python code which uses tkinter in Jupyter notebook. New GUI window appears
after calling the mainloop.
 Import the data by clicking on ‘Import Data’ button. This helps you to browse through the
system and select the data file.
 Enter the name of the target column in the entry widget bar beside ‘Target Column’ and
click on ‘Import Target’.
 Train the Neural Network Regressor model using ‘Train Model’ button given after
‘Regression’.
 Save the Neural Network Regressor model using ‘Save Model’ button given after ‘Pickle R-
model’.
 Similarly, train the Neural Network Regressor model using ‘Train Model’ button given after
‘Classifier’.
 Save the Neural Network Regressor model using ‘Save Model’ button given after ‘Pickle C-
model’.
Window 1: GUI window generated using tkinter after calling the mainloop.
Window 2: Selecting the datafile to be used for the project.
Window 3: Importing of dataset completed.
Window 4: Incorrect target column name entered.
Window 5: Correct target column found.
Window 6: Neural Network Regressor model trained.
Window 7: Neural Network Regressor model saved for future use.
Window 8: Neural Network Classifier model trained.
Window 9: Neural Network Classifier model saved for future use.
